data.chText: 人造黄油； 人造奶油
data.enText: a yellow substance like butter made from animal or vegetable fats, used in cooking or spread on bread, etc.

tr: a spread made chiefly from vegetable oils and used as a substitute for butter

value.def: Margarine is a yellow substance made from vegetable oil and animal fats that is similar to butter. You spread it on bread or use it for cooking.
